CREATE A FRONTEND OF A MOVIE RECOMMENDATION SYSTEM

Of course. I'll create a sleek and modern frontend for a movie recommendation system. This will be a visually-rich, single-page interface that you can later connect to a backend service.

Here is the design I've put together. It's a fully responsive HTML and Tailwind CSS application, featuring a dynamic layout with movie cards and categories. I've used placeholder images to give you a clear idea of the final look.

Movie Recommendation System Frontend
Jul 13, 10:47 PM

This provides a solid foundation for your project. The next steps would involve integrating a movie database API (like TMDB) to fetch real movie data and building a recommendation engine on your backend to power the "Top Picks" section.

You can easily customize the colors, fonts, and layout by modifying the Tailwind CSS classes directly in the HTML. Let me know if you'd like any adjustments or have other features in mind!
